E_PPC.dt_PlantAlarms;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t//Plant alarms struct\n\tHSL\t\t\t\t\t: REAL;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t//[pu], High sustainable limit\n\tRedundancySts\t\t: TBE_PPC.dt_RedundancyDiagnostics;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t//Redundancy status structure of local controller\n\tRemoteCtrlInputs\t: TBE_PPC.dt_RemoteCtrlInputs;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t//Inputs from remote controller\n\tPSp_PV\t\t\t\t: REAL;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t//PV active power setpoint\n\tPSp_POI\t\t\t\t: REAL;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t//POI active power setpoint\n\tPSp_Diagnostics\t\t: TBE_PPC.dt_PSpDiagnostics;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t//Diagnostics structure\nEND_VAR\nVAR_OUTPUT\n\tPlantPCmdOut_pu\t\t: REAL; \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t//[pu], Plant level real power command\n\tDiagnostics\t\t\t: TBE_PPC.dt_PCtrlDiagnostics;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t//Real power control diagnostics structure\nEND_VAR\nVAR\n\tPV_PI\t: fb_PI;    \t\t\t// PI loop\n\trlim1:TBE_PPC.fb_R_LIM; \t\t// ramp rate control\n\tFCtl:TBE_PPC.fb_F_Ctl;\t\t\t//Frequency Control\n\tExFilter1:fb_ExpFilter;\t\t\t//Process Variable filter\n\tExFilter4:fb_ExpFilter;\t\t\t//Process Variable filter\n\ttmp_ForceEn \t: BOOL;\nEND_VAR","LineInfoPersistence":"(string)b6cb46ab-0f2f-4e56-b20e-95f65d521ac4_Decl_LineIds"}}}},"UniqueIdGenerator":"(string)489","POULevel":{"@Type":"8e575c5b:Enum","@Value":"Standard"},"ChildObjectGuids":{"@Type":"ArrayList:IList","@Value":[]},"AddAttributeSubsequent":"(bool)False"}},"TypeInfos":{"0db3d7bb":"{0db3d7bb-cde0-4416-9a7b-ce49a0124323}","233bc97c":"{233bc97c-69fe-4d29-b40e-a9a9b854044e}","24449d48":"{24449d48-c96a-49c4-b9d1-a4ea34aedce3}","32d3375e":"{32d3375e-c010-41e2-9e43-b2fbf4f2b374}","3487d131":"{3487d131-7fd4-48ac-9e99-9e275c3b8ff8}","4b8bcc79":"{4b8bcc79-5980-4868-b49e-005a8148859b}","4f1e43e3":"{4f1e43e3-0667-4421-ad70-d7adf37c167a}","584effbc":"{584effbc-813e-443a-bf78-ad9c8d49db41}","5ae2e111":"{5ae2e111-ecff-4a21-b647-2d4da63f8db7}","5c3476a8":"{5c3476a8-05c5-430e-861c-9cfa51d68ca8}","65582d84":"{65582d84-cf18-4c